 Registration starts at 17:30. Entries are R30 per athlete and entrance is R5. Medals are available to all who complete the race.
There will be several stalls like NWK, Newest Technology and New Holland. Don’t eat at home because stalls with eats and drinks are available, like the well-known hospice pancakes, Rotary Anns’ hamburgers and cold drinks from Twizza.
The paramedics from MpumaCare will also be there for any emergencies. Stalls are available at R300 per stall. For more information call Elbie Helberg on 082 428 4156 or Anita Roos on 082 374 7671.
